introduction: Season 2 – Join Actor Jay Ellis as he travels the world to visit three architectural marvels per episode, and describes the story of each building’s design and construction. Each structure pushes a boundary – engineering, construction, materials, politics, etc. – and overcomes obstacles to become a standout star of the built environment.
